\section{Key Projects}  

\textbf{Demand Forecasting from Weather Data:} Built a forecasting pipeline using Python to analyze weather patterns and predict demand trends. ETL and modeling implemented using API ingestion, Snowflake DWH, and visualization in Power BI.  

\textbf{Real Estate Data Pipeline:} Developed a production-ready data pipeline using Python, AWS S3, Snowpipe, and Snowflake. Enabled real-time market analysis via Power BI dashboards.  

\textbf{Sentiment Analysis Engine:} Created an automated pipeline for social media sentiment monitoring using Selenium, Python (NLTK/sklearn), and classification models. Deployed reports for marketing impact analysis. (\href{https://github.com/Usama00004/Twitter-Sentiment-Analysis}{GitHub})  

\textbf{Sales & Order Prediction Dashboard:} Built dashboards and analysis pipelines for multi-year trends, including regression-based sales forecasts and dynamic drilldowns. (\href{https://github.com/Usama00004/DAX}{GitHub})  

\textbf{Recommendation Logic Prototype:} Implemented a basic content-based recommendation system for matching users with relevant items using pandas, cosine similarity, and scikit-learn.

